cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.HC, cs.DB

This paper involves the use of machine learning models to predict the likelihood of new onset diabetes after liver transplant based on patient data. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CE (Computational Epidemiology), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.DB (Databases).
